Arabic/ English Translator and Copywriter
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 06:56:11
Ref. JB3046926
Job Description
On behalf of a multinational FMCG client we are seeking a talented Translator / Copywriter for their Riyadh Head office in Saudi Arabia.
You will be responsible for translating all the company Memos, policies, letters writing formal Arabic letters, Proof reading etc. Writing clear, persuasive, original copies. Must be able to translate and proofread content for media, magazines, websites, press release, articles etc. Amending, revising or redeveloping adverts or campaigns
Skills
•	BA in Translation, English Literature or related degree
•	Minumum 5 years' experience in general translation work, copywriting and editing
•	You must be able to write perfectly in both languages. Extensive experience in translation in Arabic & English languages
•	Excellent organizational, presentation and writing skills and ability to successfully interact across functions and at all levels of an organization.
•	Excellent communication skills in English & Arabic.
•	Able to work under pressure and meet target deadlines
